						               													<description>Champions of Akathena: Blood and Magic is an exciting, fantasy combat board game that uses the Champions Combat System. This complete boxed game contains everything two to six players need to start playing out exciting tabletop battles, including a complete copy of the core Champions Combat System&amp;trade; rules.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Set in the fantastical, war-torn world of Akathena, this boxed set contains maps for two different battlefields, the Lockfire Swamp and the Kaladar Arena. Players will be able to choose from six different champions who hail from these lands, each with their associated reinforcements. The Marshal and his two Swordsmen hail from the Kaladar Arena, as does the Dual Wielder and the pair of Archers who accompany him, and the Dashing Swordsman and the Imperial Guard who fights beside him. In opposition to these skilled warriors, the Elementalist and his trio of Stone Constructs are native to the Lockfire Swamp, as is the Dryad Witch and her Wood Construct, and the Lizardfolk Queen and her entourage of three Lizardfolk Warriors.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As a Champions Combat System game, Champions of Akathena: Blood and Magic seamlessly integrates with all other games built using the same system, including Champions of Akathena: Into the Wild.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
